FBIS4-19421 "drweu074_b_94002" FBIS-WEU-94-074 Daily Report 15 Apr 1994 BENELUX COUNTRIES Belgium Permission for Departure Unconfirmed Permission for Departure Unconfirmed BR1504122494 Brussels Radio 1 Network in Dutch 1100 GMT 15 Apr 94 BR1504122494 Brussels Radio 1 Network Dutch BFN [Report by Guy Polspoel, Brussels BRT Television Network reporter, at Kigali airport -- live] [Excerpt] [passage omitted] [Polspoel] The blue helmets reportedly received permission to depart, considering the situation here. That is what a colleague from LE SOIR is shouting right now. And that is supposed to be the final decision. [Studio announcer] That was Guy Polspoel, with whom we talked over the phone 15 minutes ago. This announcement has not been confirmed in Brussels . On the contrary, it is said here that there has been no formal confirmation by the Security Council in New York.
